WEBVTT

00:00:10.825 --> 00:00:12.625
We need justice.

00:00:12.625 --> 00:00:16.265
Bring our people back.

00:00:16.265 --> 00:00:19.545
We need justice.

00:00:19.545 --> 00:00:23.105
Bring our people back.

00:00:23.305 --> 00:00:25.665
Hey! I said get out.

00:00:25.665 --> 00:00:27.985
Hurry up.. Get out of the building

00:00:28.945 --> 00:00:30.385
Hey!

00:00:33.265 --> 00:00:34.865
Hey! You guys.

00:00:34.865 --> 00:00:36.225
Get out of the building!

00:00:37.865 --> 00:00:39.585
Quick!

00:00:39.585 --> 00:00:41.265
Go go!

00:00:41.265 --> 00:00:42.545
Hurry up.

00:00:44.065 --> 00:00:45.265
Get out!

00:00:46.785 --> 00:00:47.865
There is no one left here.

00:00:47.865 --> 00:00:48.985
Hurry up! Quick!

00:00:48.985 --> 00:00:50.385
Go go go!

00:00:51.865 --> 00:00:53.505
How are things now, Ravin? Have you cleared everyone out?

00:00:53.505 --> 00:00:54.385
Done. Go!

00:00:55.105 --> 00:00:55.785
Hurry up!

00:00:57.305 --> 00:00:58.665
I think there's no one here.

00:01:02.945 --> 00:01:04.065
You two, go check at the back building.

00:01:04.065 --> 00:01:04.745
Where'd you go?

00:01:04.745 --> 00:01:05.745
I'll check the leaders.

00:01:05.785 --> 00:01:07.025
Wait, Ravin.

00:01:07.025 --> 00:01:07.705
Be careful.

00:01:08.585 --> 00:01:09.225
Come, Mada.

00:01:14.105 --> 00:01:15.105
Go around that way.

00:01:15.105 --> 00:01:16.425
What about the Law building?

00:01:16.465 --> 00:01:17.665
There's no one left at the Law building.

00:01:17.705 --> 00:01:19.105
I'll check at the Social Sciences building.

00:01:19.105 --> 00:01:20.425
I'll check at the Accountancy building.

00:01:20.465 --> 00:01:20.985
OK.

00:01:20.985 --> 00:01:21.865
Be careful.

00:01:44.665 --> 00:01:45.665
Mai!

00:02:08.505 --> 00:02:09.505
Stop

00:02:42.985 --> 00:02:44.185
Hello.

00:02:49.945 --> 00:02:51.145
What?

00:03:02.265 --> 00:03:05.025
Remember to go to the meeting point when you get out.

00:03:14.745 --> 00:03:18.665
Our friends out there are preparing to go to the forest.

00:03:19.625 --> 00:03:21.385
If we want to reform the country,

00:03:21.385 --> 00:03:23.865
we must go where there's opportunity.

00:03:25.225 --> 00:03:26.745
Do you want to join us?

00:03:38.425 --> 00:03:39.905
If so, what do I have to do?

00:03:40.705 --> 00:03:42.465
I'll tell you where to meet later.

00:03:54.945 --> 00:03:58.585
Lt. Det, could you allow me to see my son?

00:04:01.025 --> 00:04:02.625
Please, Lt.

00:04:04.025 --> 00:04:04.745
Sure, teacher.

00:04:04.745 --> 00:04:05.465
Thanks so much.

00:04:07.865 --> 00:04:08.585
Vin.

00:04:09.865 --> 00:04:10.585
Mom.

00:04:11.265 --> 00:04:12.705
Vin, are you ok?

00:04:16.505 --> 00:04:17.985
Did you get hurt?

00:04:21.145 --> 00:04:23.225
I'll try to bail you out.

00:04:25.745 --> 00:04:26.745
All of you, too.

00:04:32.665 --> 00:04:33.625
Please calm down.

00:04:34.905 --> 00:04:36.305
I'm here for the arrested students.

00:04:39.105 --> 00:04:39.825
This way.

00:05:55.825 --> 00:05:57.625
Dan told me he'll come tomorrow.

00:05:59.225 --> 00:06:01.385
Don't forget to thank him properly.

00:06:02.785 --> 00:06:04.505
If it wasn't for him,

00:06:07.065 --> 00:06:09.905
I wouldn't know how to get you out.

00:06:12.105 --> 00:06:13.225
OK, mom.

00:06:17.265 --> 00:06:18.905
He moved away a long time ago

00:06:20.625 --> 00:06:23.505
Never thought I’d see him helping us.

00:06:25.585 --> 00:06:26.785
Guess we’re lucky.

00:06:27.905 --> 00:06:34.065
..have fled into the jungle to join the Communist Party of Thailand.

00:06:35.225 --> 00:06:39.465
Such actions are considered a grave threat to national security.

00:06:39.465 --> 00:06:42.425
I don't want you to join this.

00:06:43.985 --> 00:06:46.545
Your duty is to study.

00:06:46.545 --> 00:06:49.145
Leave the national affairs to the others.

00:06:53.705 --> 00:06:55.585
Mom.

00:06:55.665 --> 00:06:57.585
I just want to make this country better.

00:07:00.065 --> 00:07:02.225
I went to the volunteer camp in the countryside.

00:07:04.225 --> 00:07:05.545
There's a lot of exploitation out there.

00:07:06.265 --> 00:07:07.505
Inequality is everywhere.

00:07:07.785 --> 00:07:11.545
I know you want to make our country better,

00:07:15.025 --> 00:07:17.305
but there are many methods to do that.

00:07:17.305 --> 00:07:19.665
Please don't follow the trend.

00:07:19.905 --> 00:07:22.265
There's no need to go to the protest like this.

00:07:26.185 --> 00:07:27.665
Do you get me?

00:07:30.465 --> 00:07:31.465
Yes I do.

00:08:22.745 --> 00:08:23.745
My friends and I..

00:08:24.985 --> 00:08:26.665
we might just be small, ordinary people.

00:08:27.945 --> 00:08:29.585
But our hearts are 'great'

00:08:30.585 --> 00:08:35.185
enough to believe that equality must exist.

00:08:36.105 --> 00:08:37.785
No matter how much we must endure.

00:08:38.745 --> 00:08:40.385
Because the people we love most..

00:08:41.385 --> 00:08:43.025
deserve to live in a better world.

00:08:45.825 --> 00:08:49.065
My name is Ravin. It means 'The Sun'.

00:08:50.425 --> 00:08:52.865
The sun’s duty isn’t just to shine,

00:08:52.985 --> 00:08:55.465
it’s to give light to everyone, equally.

00:08:57.105 --> 00:08:58.785
And true light..

00:08:59.385 --> 00:09:01.105
doesn’t shine for itself;

00:09:01.705 --> 00:09:03.745
it shines so that others can see the way.

00:09:04.745 --> 00:09:07.785
Even the smallest people can be a 'Great Sun'

00:09:08.385 --> 00:09:09.785
for someone else.

00:09:24.145 --> 00:09:25.545
Get off, kids.

00:09:35.185 --> 00:09:36.145
Ouch!

00:09:38.985 --> 00:09:40.345
Are we here?

00:09:40.705 --> 00:09:42.065
Just answer this if you meet anyone.

00:09:42.785 --> 00:09:45.025
"Though the sky is dark, the stars remain."

00:09:47.625 --> 00:09:48.825
Yes sir.

00:09:48.825 --> 00:09:49.905
Keep it quiet.

00:10:02.105 --> 00:10:03.185
What's next?

00:10:08.585 --> 00:10:09.465
Who?

00:10:14.625 --> 00:10:15.505
Who?

00:10:17.025 --> 00:10:17.985
We...

00:10:18.585 --> 00:10:20.665
Though the sky is dark, the stars remain.

00:10:40.225 --> 00:10:41.385
Is that all of you?

00:10:43.905 --> 00:10:46.905
Good, let's go.

00:10:48.705 --> 00:10:50.585
Uh... wait a moment.

00:10:50.985 --> 00:10:51.985
I...

00:10:52.585 --> 00:10:53.825
I have a stomachache.

00:10:53.825 --> 00:10:55.065
Poo?

00:10:56.625 --> 00:10:57.825
Stomachache.

00:10:58.105 --> 00:10:58.785
Just wait a moment.

00:10:58.905 --> 00:11:01.505
If you want to poo. Go there.

00:11:02.985 --> 00:11:04.265
The rest will wait here.

00:11:05.305 --> 00:11:06.465
Any tissue paper?

00:11:06.465 --> 00:11:10.065
Nope! Who uses tissue paper in the forest?

00:11:12.505 --> 00:11:13.705
Beware of the soldier.

00:11:14.705 --> 00:11:16.225
Beware of the soldier.

00:11:22.025 --> 00:11:24.985
Phew! Almost didn't make it.

00:11:31.625 --> 00:11:33.425
Do I really need leaves to wipe my ass?

00:11:37.865 --> 00:11:38.985
Whatever.

00:11:40.785 --> 00:11:43.465
Ouch!

00:12:07.385 --> 00:12:08.505
Which way?

00:12:24.025 --> 00:12:25.185
Ouch!

00:12:26.745 --> 00:12:32.185
Ouch!!

00:12:54.065 --> 00:12:55.185
Get up!

00:12:57.585 --> 00:12:58.745
Get up!

00:12:59.145 --> 00:13:00.345
Sorry.

00:13:02.425 --> 00:13:04.145
Thank you so much for saving me.

00:13:06.345 --> 00:13:09.345
Be careful if you don't want to die in the forest

00:13:10.265 --> 00:13:12.385
Thank you so much for saving me.

00:13:13.145 --> 00:13:14.505
My name is Ravin.

00:13:16.865 --> 00:13:18.465
You can call me Vin.

00:13:22.105 --> 00:13:23.505
What do you want me to call you?

00:13:31.025 --> 00:13:31.945
Comrade Yue.

00:13:34.785 --> 00:13:38.185
Yeh... Yoh... Yeh... Yeow...

00:13:38.185 --> 00:13:39.065
Yue.

00:13:39.065 --> 00:13:39.905
Yea.

00:13:39.905 --> 00:13:40.785
Yue.

00:13:41.545 --> 00:13:42.385
Yeah...

00:13:42.385 --> 00:13:43.145
Yeww.

00:13:43.145 --> 00:13:44.025
Yue.

00:13:44.025 --> 00:13:44.865
Yea.

00:13:44.865 --> 00:13:45.745
Comrade Yue.

00:13:46.905 --> 00:13:47.785
Yeww.

00:13:52.825 --> 00:13:53.665
Yak.

00:13:55.785 --> 00:13:56.665
Stop.

00:13:57.505 --> 00:13:59.625
Keep quiet, just follow me.

00:14:03.425 --> 00:14:06.545
Yes, Comrade Yak.

00:14:07.465 --> 00:14:10.305
What kind of person lacks social skills.

00:14:19.905 --> 00:14:21.625
I think he's been gone too long.

00:14:21.865 --> 00:14:23.385
I'm gonna go find him.

00:14:24.785 --> 00:14:26.865
Please take care of the students

00:14:27.265 --> 00:14:28.145
Yes sir.

00:14:30.985 --> 00:14:33.825
Hey! Why do you take this path, comrade?

00:14:33.825 --> 00:14:35.945
What about the path you explored?

00:14:39.745 --> 00:14:41.905
Why do you come together?

00:14:45.265 --> 00:14:47.345
Everyone is here. Let's go.

00:14:53.625 --> 00:14:55.265
What took you so long?

00:14:56.145 --> 00:14:57.465
I got a little lost.

00:14:58.265 --> 00:14:59.585
I tripped.

00:15:00.265 --> 00:15:03.065
Luckily, Yak saved me.

00:15:03.825 --> 00:15:06.065
Yak? Is that the name?

00:15:07.065 --> 00:15:08.025
Yep.

00:15:09.985 --> 00:15:12.025
What the hell...Yak?

00:15:12.865 --> 00:15:16.545
What a weird name. Yak? Seriously?

00:15:16.865 --> 00:15:18.705
Yes it is.

00:15:56.905 --> 00:15:58.945
My legs are dragging. When will I get there?

00:15:59.225 --> 00:16:00.545
Exactly.

00:16:02.545 --> 00:16:03.865
Ouch!

00:16:06.865 --> 00:16:08.185
Let me carry your bag.

00:16:15.945 --> 00:16:19.265
Have some water first. It’ll help you feel better.

00:16:21.585 --> 00:16:23.105
Can I have some? I'm all out.

00:16:29.625 --> 00:16:31.145
Umm.

00:16:49.185 --> 00:16:50.705
Yak.

00:16:51.185 --> 00:16:52.545
Yak.

00:16:53.065 --> 00:16:54.145
Yak, Yak.

00:16:56.065 --> 00:16:56.905
How far?

00:16:58.585 --> 00:17:01.745
A bit more.. just go over that mountain.

00:17:03.865 --> 00:17:05.985
The mountain? A bit more?

00:17:07.985 --> 00:17:08.945
Yak.

00:17:10.105 --> 00:17:11.625
How far do we have to go to reach the base?

00:17:14.505 --> 00:17:17.065
I think you're tired because you're talking too much.

00:17:18.225 --> 00:17:19.585
Just shut up and keep walking.

00:17:20.345 --> 00:17:23.905
We've been tired. Can we have a little break?

00:17:33.065 --> 00:17:34.425
If you can’t take only this.

00:17:35.545 --> 00:17:36.905
You should go back to the university, right?

00:17:46.385 --> 00:17:47.745
Give it to her.

00:17:51.745 --> 00:17:54.745
There's a stream up ahead, don't stop yet.

00:17:56.585 --> 00:17:58.665
Fine, just a bit more.

00:18:01.625 --> 00:18:02.985
Hey!

00:18:03.265 --> 00:18:05.865
Drink first. Hang in there.

00:18:05.865 --> 00:18:06.705
He said...

00:18:07.465 --> 00:18:09.305
A-BIT-MORE.

00:18:10.905 --> 00:18:11.345
Go.

00:18:30.345 --> 00:18:31.305
Everyone.

00:18:32.345 --> 00:18:33.305
Tonight we will take a rest here.

00:18:35.545 --> 00:18:36.505
Phew!

00:19:11.705 --> 00:19:12.665
Everyone is ready to eat.

00:19:16.865 --> 00:19:19.225
Go ahead. I just wanna rest here for a while.

00:19:20.105 --> 00:19:22.225
If you want to stay together in the base, stick to the rules.

00:19:25.505 --> 00:19:27.305
When it’s time to eat, you eat.

00:19:27.705 --> 00:19:29.505
When it’s time to work, you work.

00:19:31.025 --> 00:19:32.705
Don’t just do whatever you feel like.

00:19:33.345 --> 00:19:36.465
Yes sir, Comrade Yak.

00:20:05.345 --> 00:20:06.825
Why do you have to be so forceful?

00:20:09.025 --> 00:20:10.785
Why can't you see the big anthill?

00:20:18.305 --> 00:20:19.985
If it’s a mine, you’d be done for.

00:20:39.865 --> 00:20:41.145
This is for you.

00:20:41.945 --> 00:20:43.905
Thank you.

00:20:44.065 --> 00:20:45.425
Mr.?

00:20:46.585 --> 00:20:49.465
Just call me Yaguar. I'm only a volunteered villager.

00:20:50.625 --> 00:20:51.825
Thank you.

00:20:51.825 --> 00:20:53.145
Yes.

00:20:58.825 --> 00:21:00.145
Hey!

00:21:00.265 --> 00:21:04.585
Come here, come come.

00:21:05.065 --> 00:21:06.065
Come here. Sit together.

00:21:06.985 --> 00:21:08.105
Hurry up, comrade.

00:21:08.505 --> 00:21:10.065
Sit here.

00:21:17.105 --> 00:21:18.265
Eat it.

00:21:24.265 --> 00:21:26.785
It's OK. I can sit with my friends.

00:21:28.065 --> 00:21:29.425
So you can eat your fill.

00:21:30.425 --> 00:21:31.665
You can share with me.

00:21:32.905 --> 00:21:34.225
Why share?

00:21:34.625 --> 00:21:36.025
We got equally tired walking,

00:21:36.025 --> 00:21:37.385
so we should eat equally.

00:21:39.065 --> 00:21:40.265
Then we’ll have enough strength to walk.

00:21:41.145 --> 00:21:42.105
Eat it.

00:21:51.745 --> 00:21:53.145
What is this meat? It tastes gamey.

00:21:56.225 --> 00:21:57.185
It's dog meat.

00:22:02.705 --> 00:22:04.465
We're in a forest, not in a city.

00:22:05.185 --> 00:22:07.345
We eat to live,

00:22:07.905 --> 00:22:09.345
not live to eat.

00:22:15.825 --> 00:22:16.745
Eat it.

00:22:22.145 --> 00:22:23.105
Sila.

00:22:25.985 --> 00:22:28.825
As they said, we have to adjust to living.

00:22:29.265 --> 00:22:30.385
If we can't bear just this.

00:22:30.985 --> 00:22:32.305
how will we handle tougher things?

00:22:34.025 --> 00:22:35.905
It might be rough at first.

00:22:37.185 --> 00:22:39.865
You should try to eat. It's cold at night.

00:22:39.865 --> 00:22:41.345
Dog meat can keep you warm.

00:23:07.905 --> 00:23:08.745
Mada.

00:23:12.265 --> 00:23:16.625
It's not easy to find food in the forest. If it's edible, eat it.

00:23:16.625 --> 00:23:19.865
Please don't be a burden to others.

00:23:24.505 --> 00:23:25.305
Is it too harsh?

00:23:27.905 --> 00:23:28.705
It's alright, Mada.

00:23:30.465 --> 00:23:31.585
Go take a seat.

00:23:45.425 --> 00:23:47.905
Try harder, so you’ll have the strength.

00:23:53.825 --> 00:23:56.505
Come here, sit with us.

00:23:56.505 --> 00:23:57.865
I want to sit with my friends.

00:23:57.865 --> 00:23:58.745
Nope.

00:23:58.745 --> 00:23:59.705
Sit with Mada.

00:23:59.705 --> 00:24:00.585
Nope.

00:24:00.585 --> 00:24:02.545
Sit down.

00:24:04.145 --> 00:24:05.065
Eat it.

00:24:05.545 --> 00:24:07.705
Try harder, so you’ll have the strength.

00:24:11.985 --> 00:24:16.225
Yummy! I've never ever tasted it before.

00:24:17.025 --> 00:24:18.785
So delicious, very delicious.

00:24:19.065 --> 00:24:23.225
Good. So finish it. Tomorrow you have to walk a lot.

00:24:32.105 --> 00:24:33.065
Fine! I will.

00:24:44.025 --> 00:24:46.025
Vin has been gone a couple of days.

00:24:47.065 --> 00:24:51.225
I asked Mada's mom. She told me...

00:24:52.625 --> 00:24:54.665
Mada has been gone with Sila as well.

00:24:58.745 --> 00:25:00.465
I'm afraid, Dan.

00:25:04.785 --> 00:25:06.825
I'm afraid that Vin would go to the forest.

00:25:15.345 --> 00:25:17.065
Don't worry, Aunt La-or.

00:25:17.945 --> 00:25:19.785
I'll find out about Vin.

00:25:20.585 --> 00:25:22.465
And will call you as soon as I get the information.

00:25:28.985 --> 00:25:30.465
Let me pick up the phone.

00:25:30.505 --> 00:25:31.305
Sure.

00:26:02.465 --> 00:26:04.665
Vin.

00:26:05.465 --> 00:26:07.665
Are you hurt?

00:26:08.105 --> 00:26:10.505
Don't worry. You will be fine.

00:26:10.505 --> 00:26:12.025
Go take some rest there.

00:26:19.745 --> 00:26:21.225
Eat this, Dan.

00:26:22.785 --> 00:26:24.225
It's good. You should try some.

00:26:25.145 --> 00:26:26.585
Eat more, so you can grow faster.

00:26:40.985 --> 00:26:42.465
I'll bring you home, Vin.

00:27:22.585 --> 00:27:27.945
New Student List: Baan Saeng Dao Base

00:27:30.705 --> 00:27:32.905
Comrade Ploeng, do you know Ravin ShineShan's background?

00:27:34.185 --> 00:27:35.745
Have you been thinking about it?

00:27:37.225 --> 00:27:39.505
Having the same last name or being siblings,

00:27:39.505 --> 00:27:41.625
doesn't mean they know each other.

00:27:42.465 --> 00:27:45.425
Whatever happens out there, stays out there.

00:27:46.305 --> 00:27:48.225
Our ideology here is more important.

00:27:59.425 --> 00:28:04.785
Ravin and his two friends who are student leaders,are interesting.

00:28:05.345 --> 00:28:07.985
They have passion and determination,

00:28:08.265 --> 00:28:10.225
and can really help us with this mission.

00:28:22.705 --> 00:28:26.745
We need justice.

00:28:26.745 --> 00:28:30.345
Bring our people back.

00:28:30.345 --> 00:28:33.545
We need justice.

00:28:33.545 --> 00:28:37.185
Bring our people back.

00:28:37.185 --> 00:28:38.465
We have no weapons.

00:28:38.985 --> 00:28:40.305
Don't shoot us.

00:28:40.305 --> 00:28:41.785
Don't shoot our people.

00:28:44.865 --> 00:28:47.105
Help me, Vin.

00:29:21.345 --> 00:29:22.065
Crying?

00:29:38.465 --> 00:29:39.545
I have a bad dream.

00:29:42.905 --> 00:29:44.625
I dream about the university that day.

00:29:52.425 --> 00:29:53.945
I dream about the university that day.

00:29:57.945 --> 00:29:59.865
Now you've chosen to be here in the forest.

00:30:01.745 --> 00:30:03.225
So please stick to the ideology.

00:30:04.505 --> 00:30:05.825
Then, follow our revolutionary path.

00:30:14.105 --> 00:30:15.425
I know it's not that easy.

00:30:17.945 --> 00:30:19.265
But that doesn't mean it's impossible.

00:30:22.025 --> 00:30:23.145
I've been through it before.

00:30:30.385 --> 00:30:31.465
How did you get through it?

00:30:37.505 --> 00:30:38.705
You'll see.

00:30:43.945 --> 00:30:46.345
Get some sleep, we’ve got a long way to go tomorrow.

00:30:52.785 --> 00:30:54.585
Thank for taking care of me.

00:31:52.825 --> 00:31:54.105
Are you OK, Mada?

00:32:04.305 --> 00:32:05.705
How far does it take to reach the base?

00:32:05.705 --> 00:32:06.785
Almost there.

00:32:12.345 --> 00:32:13.665
Mr. Yak said it's just a bit.

00:32:15.025 --> 00:32:16.345
But I think it means a mountain.

00:32:16.985 --> 00:32:20.025
Just keep walking. I'm too tired to talk.

00:32:23.745 --> 00:32:25.145
That kid is really mischievous.

00:32:35.945 --> 00:32:38.185
This is it. The entrance of our base.

00:33:16.865 --> 00:33:22.145
With the upcountry surrounding the city, the people must prevail.

00:33:25.945 --> 00:33:28.185
The newbie young comrades arrive!

00:33:46.025 --> 00:33:49.625
Welcome to Baan Saeng Dao’s base, comrades.

00:33:54.065 --> 00:33:57.705
One of the allies of Communist Party of Thailand.

00:33:58.465 --> 00:34:00.145
Welcome.

00:34:01.865 --> 00:34:05.505
Yes! We're here.

00:34:05.505 --> 00:34:06.985
Finally we make it!

00:35:03.465 --> 00:35:07.945
Comrades, victory belongs to the people.

00:35:08.705 --> 00:35:11.105
Hello again, every new comrade.

00:35:12.665 --> 00:35:15.225
From now on we are one family.

00:35:15.985 --> 00:35:18.585
We stay together as comrades.

00:35:19.705 --> 00:35:24.025
We'll share joy, pain, and the same ideology.

00:35:24.505 --> 00:35:26.825
Whatever happens outside, stays outside.

00:35:26.825 --> 00:35:31.145
Here, we won’t ask about your past or background.

00:35:31.745 --> 00:35:33.265
For security,

00:35:33.665 --> 00:35:36.985
We will use an alias instead of our real name.

00:35:38.785 --> 00:35:41.705
if anyone already has one in mind, tell us.

00:35:43.785 --> 00:35:45.705
I will go by Comrade Gaun Hin.

00:35:45.745 --> 00:35:48.945
I want to be like a rock. Stay strong and unshakable for our country.

00:35:49.385 --> 00:35:52.065
Mhm, good!

00:35:55.305 --> 00:35:56.865
This one will go by Comrade Meut.

00:35:57.785 --> 00:35:59.345
This one will go by Comrade Dum.

00:35:59.665 --> 00:36:04.065
Mhm, Comrade Meut, Comrade Dum. Great!

00:36:05.625 --> 00:36:06.505
Who's Ravin

00:36:08.785 --> 00:36:09.905
When did you create the alias?

00:36:10.785 --> 00:36:11.905
The one who's talking to Comrade Gaun Hin.

00:36:14.825 --> 00:36:16.745
People need to be prepared.

00:36:20.145 --> 00:36:21.145
Do you think he is involved with that guy?

00:36:23.625 --> 00:36:24.625
Don't know yet.

00:36:27.185 --> 00:36:28.385
What about you two?

00:36:30.825 --> 00:36:32.225
We haven't thought anything yet.

00:36:33.825 --> 00:36:36.465
Well, you go by Comrade Ying.

00:36:39.305 --> 00:36:41.905
Good. Thank you, Comrade Ploeng.

00:36:42.385 --> 00:36:43.425
What about you?

00:36:45.425 --> 00:36:46.545
He is Comrade Saeng.

00:36:53.145 --> 00:36:56.625
all right, Comrade Saeng. Then it's settled.

00:36:56.825 --> 00:36:58.905
All of the new comrade

00:36:58.905 --> 00:37:01.265
please get your personal belongings at the quartermaster.

00:37:01.505 --> 00:37:06.665
We will treat each other with honor, and respect here.

00:37:08.225 --> 00:37:10.385
Shit! I don't like the name 'Comrade Saeng', so lame.

00:37:11.865 --> 00:37:17.065
We do not use swear words here. Not even “shit” or “damn.”

00:37:19.265 --> 00:37:20.305
Shit! Me again.

00:37:22.185 --> 00:37:23.745
He's just said that no "shit."

00:37:25.145 --> 00:37:28.145
If we're all clear, dismissed.

00:37:38.025 --> 00:37:41.665
Hey Comrade! Take it.

00:37:44.265 --> 00:37:46.545
Hand everything out.

00:37:46.545 --> 00:37:48.825
I don't like the name "Comrade Saeng."

00:37:50.825 --> 00:37:52.145
Comrade.

00:37:56.945 --> 00:37:58.065
Wait a minute. I'll be back.

00:37:59.545 --> 00:38:03.225
Yak. Yak. Yak.

00:38:04.305 --> 00:38:07.225
Yak. Yak.

00:38:10.705 --> 00:38:13.305
We already have a title. You can call me a comrade.

00:38:13.305 --> 00:38:15.785
Sure, Comrade Yak.

00:38:16.025 --> 00:38:17.665
Please pronounce it correctly.

00:38:19.665 --> 00:38:27.585
Comrade Yue... Comrade Yue! Comrade Yue!

00:38:44.345 --> 00:38:45.945
Why are you hanging around me?

00:38:46.665 --> 00:38:51.505
I want to know why do you pick "Comrade Saeng"? It's so outdated, and lame.

00:38:53.345 --> 00:39:00.025
It suits you. Doesn't your real name mean "the sun"?

00:39:05.785 --> 00:39:09.625
Urgh!!!

00:39:09.865 --> 00:39:12.185
Thank you so much for saving me.

00:39:12.185 --> 00:39:15.385
My name is Ravin. You can call me Vin

00:39:16.105 --> 00:39:18.225
Oh, from when I took a dump.

00:39:18.225 --> 00:39:22.225
Hey Comrade! Hurry up and take it.

00:39:37.105 --> 00:39:39.145
Yay!

00:39:39.185 --> 00:39:40.145
I'd go with that one over there.

00:39:40.145 --> 00:39:42.145
Ugh... Argh!

00:39:42.705 --> 00:39:44.385
Hey! Fine, It's yours. I'll take the other one.

00:39:48.785 --> 00:39:51.305
Let's see what we've got here..

00:39:53.545 --> 00:39:55.185
Whoa, there’s a flashlight!

00:39:56.265 --> 00:39:57.865
Mmmm.. A flashlight.

00:40:07.185 --> 00:40:08.505
Are you OK, Comrade Saeng?

00:40:12.305 --> 00:40:15.505
Hey Comrade Saeng! Don't you hear me?

00:40:18.865 --> 00:40:21.385
Comrade Gaun Hin is speaking to you, Comrade Saeng.

00:40:22.505 --> 00:40:24.545
Shit! Did you call me?

00:40:26.545 --> 00:40:31.025
No more "shit". You were just named "Comrade Saeng." Did you forget?

00:40:32.745 --> 00:40:35.905
Sorry. I forget.

00:40:37.785 --> 00:40:39.505
What are you trying to say?

00:40:39.505 --> 00:40:43.145
I asked you, "Are you OK with it?"

00:40:43.145 --> 00:40:47.465
Oh, that's it? No need to make it sound so formal. That's easy.

00:40:52.385 --> 00:40:55.385
Are you done with your belongings? So go take a shower.

00:40:55.585 --> 00:40:56.505
Finished.

00:40:56.505 --> 00:40:57.705
Go take a shower.

00:41:00.225 --> 00:41:02.785
Go take a shower. We're so stinky.

00:41:20.145 --> 00:41:21.065
Get down.

00:41:21.065 --> 00:41:24.025
Woohoo!

00:41:24.025 --> 00:41:26.585
Finally, it’s shower time! I’m so stinky.

00:41:26.585 --> 00:41:27.665
Yay!

00:41:27.665 --> 00:41:28.585
Woohoo!

00:41:28.585 --> 00:41:29.545
Woohoo!

00:41:30.865 --> 00:41:32.425
This is not a playground.

00:41:34.305 --> 00:41:38.345
If your noise drowns out the warning siren, you won’t escape in time.

00:41:39.025 --> 00:41:40.145
Especially you

00:41:41.665 --> 00:41:44.465
What the hell? Why me?